CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, February 10, 1962, pg. 20A reads: "Dapper Dollies - Among hostesses at the Dapper Dan banquet were (left to right): Norma Small, Georgia White and Carmen Sabo, who was crowned "Dapper Dan Queen." - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Group portrait of hostesses Norma Small, Georgia White, and "Queen" Carmen Sabo, posed in interior for Dapper Dan banquet
